data.description: Solid Stone & Stucco Rancher! They don't build them like this anymore. Lots of living space with this home, starting with a formal Living room with stone fireplace, formal dining room, eat-in-kitchen, 3 Bedrooms,1 bath, 2 half baths. Hardwood floors through-out, most all windows have been replaced. Full finished basement with office and bar, walk out to a 3 season room with slate floors. All this situated on almost 1/2 acre with very nice landscaping. Priced agressively, put this on your list of homes to see!
